Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到目标信息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三叉戟弹头直击前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到4枚Delta Foxtrot 21从吉林省通化基地发射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后 目标识别为Alpha Bravo Charlie Delta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明世界都充满了怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将系统转为BMD模式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CIC指示的目标 开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commence Fire！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离拦截目标还剩10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9 8 7
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6 5 4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰的SM-3击破目标Alpha
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾岛和美军的Shiloh也击破了Bravo和Charlie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩一枚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是分配给Curtis Wilbur的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.74,0:01:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Curtis Wilbur 这里是Kongo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何贵舰不发射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答 请回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩一发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线是去哪的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是美国吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到底发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那道光是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是警察吧 快说明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起 晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成为真正的黑暗

